{"tid":1885882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發，孫興民骨折","createTime":"2020-02-18T14:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T06:39:40.000Z","uid":62073,"like":268,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"164c635a04b3636be3d86006bf3703befec97588","tid":1885882,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"熱刺堅命途多舛，先傷哈利卡尼，依家輪到孫興民！呢名南韓國腳剛梅開二度，於英超擊敗維拉之戰做功臣，但原來佢開波31秒已經整傷右臂，成場波都忍痛作戰，賽後證實佢右臂骨折，將會接受手術，熱刺表示佢起碼要抖6-8周<br />\n<br />\n原來今場開賽31秒，孫興民同維拉後衞安斯干沙炒埋一碟，嗰陣已經整傷手臂，不過接受治療後老孫依然奮力比賽，去到半場亦都同樣要接受軍醫治理。孫興民不負所托，最後射入奠勝球，但未來數周都唔可以出場，摩連奴只得番盧卡斯莫拉1個前鋒，無論爭歐聯出線、抑或爭英超前4，都造成重大打擊。"},{"pid":"8af55a1ae85d362be9d200e8622172ac43d63fda","tid":1885882,"uid":225130,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪真名上連登<br />\n識有個熱狗同你同名"},{"pid":"3314c2813e4532ac2e4fe39a58b6e0bca0312660","tid":1885882,"uid":50124,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"果個Parrot肯出未"},{"pid":"3377bf4405f0bda35459aa4ce00003a74758a4d1","tid":1885882,"uid":62073,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8af55a1ae85d362be9d200e8622172ac43d63fda","tid":1885882,"uid":225130,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪真名上連登<br />\n識有個熱狗同你同名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff79677f101dc2c0b3772088a68da4ce25d866d","tid":1885882,"uid":42246,"like":20,"dislike":41,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"韓國人+運動抵死啦"},{"pid":"adadea2dc656675226b084dbccbcf77f6fcc3f29","tid":1885882,"uid":60432,"like":50,"dislike":4,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"踢斷人腳終於要還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3510e08f8db8aae9067e84d8bf44c498d34410dd","tid":1885882,"uid":62073,"li